description: Sauna Eucalipto Gel is great for eliminating unsightly stretch marks and cellulite.  With continued use, you can lose inches too!  Use with our specially designed plastic wrap, not regular plastic wrap.

name: Vest
description:
The vest is very similar to the corset, with the exception of two thin straps. It also comes in sizes XS to XXL. Like the corset, the vest has sturdy construction, consisting of latex and cotton. It also features steel boning, which allows the vest to maintain its shape. The vest is recommended for anyone who wants to target back fat, has had children, or simply wants extra support.

Additional Info:  
Please see the sizing chart for assistance.

Your premium quality vest should be hand washed in mild, warm water.  Hang to dry.  DO NOT MACHINE WASH OR TUMBLE DRY!
